WEBVTT

00:01.432 --> 00:02.703
PREVIOUSLY ON "REVENGE"...

00:02.703 --> 00:04.175
WE HAVE REASON TO BELIEVE
THAT YOU HAVE INFORMATION

00:04.175 --> 00:05.406
ABOUT THE ABDUCTION
OF CHARLOTTE CLARKE.

00:05.406 --> 00:06.407
WE'RE GONNA NEED YOU
TO COME DOWN TO THE STATION

00:06.407 --> 00:08.079
FOR SOME QUESTIONING.

00:08.079 --> 00:09.780
YOU ARE OFFICIALLY
MY SECOND-IN-COMMAND.

00:09.780 --> 00:11.442
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

00:11.442 --> 00:13.244
GIDEON?
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

00:13.244 --> 00:15.086
YOU'RE MY BIG SISTER
AND MY BOSS.

00:15.086 --> 00:16.617
MY SISTER STOLE THE COMPANY
OUT FROM UNDER ME.

00:16.617 --> 00:19.220
YOU TAKE THE REINS,
AND WE PARTNER UP.

00:19.220 --> 00:22.193
NOW WE HAVE THE PHOTO WE'LL USE
TO BLACKMAIL DANNY.

00:22.193 --> 00:23.424
THIS ISN'T
HOW I DO BUSINESS.

00:23.424 --> 00:25.056
WELL, IT IS NOW.

00:25.056 --> 00:26.397
Mostrowski:
PEOPLE THINK I HATE YOU,

00:26.397 --> 00:28.059
NO ONE LOOKS AT ME
WHEN YOU'RE GONE.

00:28.059 --> 00:30.701
TRANSPORTATION WILL MEET YOU
ABOUT A MILE SOUTH.

00:30.701 --> 00:32.503
DAVID?

00:32.503 --> 00:35.066
[ GRUNTING ]

00:35.066 --> 00:38.038
NOW THIS IS WHERE IT ALL ENDS.
FITTING.

00:39.540 --> 00:40.611
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

00:40.611 --> 00:41.672
YOU NEEDED HELP.

00:41.672 --> 00:43.344
I HAD NO CHOICE
BUT TO CHECK YOU IN.

00:43.344 --> 00:44.415
HELP ME!

00:44.415 --> 00:46.046
GOODBYE, VICTORIA.

00:46.046 --> 00:48.119
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!!

00:48.119 --> 00:50.081
[ Crying ]
SHE'S AMANDA CLARKE!

00:58.159 --> 01:01.432
Victoria: IN MY LIFETIME,
I'VE COME TO UNDERSTAND

01:01.432 --> 01:04.735
THAT THERE ARE THREE WAYS
FOR A PERSON TO DISAPPEAR.

01:04.735 --> 01:06.737
THE FIRST IS TO DIE.

01:06.737 --> 01:10.271
THE SECOND IS TO LIE.

01:10.271 --> 01:13.404
AND THE LAST
IS TO BE REBORN.

01:13.404 --> 01:17.748
IT WAS AFTER MY FORMER HUSBAND'S
DEATH SIX MONTHS AGO

01:17.748 --> 01:20.411
THAT MY TRANSFORMATION
BEGAN.

01:20.411 --> 01:25.116
I MADE MY PEACE
WITH THOSE WHO HAVE WRONGED ME

01:25.116 --> 01:28.259
AND WITH THOSE
WHO I'VE WRONGED,

01:28.259 --> 01:31.692
NO ONE MORE SO
THAN EMILY THORNE.

01:35.296 --> 01:37.528
THUS,
AFTER MONTHS OF DENIAL,

01:37.528 --> 01:41.132
I'VE COME TO SEE MY TIME HERE
IN CLAREMONT AS A RENAISSANCE.

01:41.132 --> 01:44.505
AND I UNDERSTAND
THAT THE TRAUMA I SUFFERED

01:44.505 --> 01:48.179
SEEING MY MURDERED FIANCé
LED TO MY DELUSIONS,

01:48.179 --> 01:49.840
FROM WHICH I'M NOW FREE.

01:49.840 --> 01:52.313
NEVER LOSE HOPE,
VICTORIA.

01:52.313 --> 01:54.315
WITH YOUR HELP, I WON'T,
PHYLLIS.

01:54.315 --> 01:58.118
AND ON THAT NOTE OF CAMARADERIE,
WE ARE DONE FOR THE MORNING.

01:58.118 --> 02:00.191
THANK YOU, LADIES.

02:05.556 --> 02:08.229
IT APPEARS
YOU'VE ACTUALLY MADE A FRIEND.

02:08.229 --> 02:10.130
OH, I'VE MADE MANY,
DR. MILLER.

02:10.130 --> 02:12.163
YOU SIMPLY HAVE SIMPLY CHOSEN
NOT TO NOTICE.

02:15.166 --> 02:18.169
WELL, PERHAPS HERE COMES
ANOTHER.

02:20.371 --> 02:22.173
[ SIGHS ]

02:22.173 --> 02:25.676
YOU KNOW, I THINK I MAY HAVE
LEFT SOMETHING BACK IN MY CAR.

02:25.676 --> 02:27.418
MA'AM, YOU CAN'T LEAVE.

02:27.418 --> 02:28.749
[ SIGHS ]

02:32.523 --> 02:33.854
YOU NEED TO COME
WITH ME.

02:33.854 --> 02:35.886
SHE HAS
QUITE AN ELEGANCE.

02:35.886 --> 02:37.358
ARE YOU SAYING
THAT I DON'T?!

02:37.358 --> 02:38.829
IS THAT
WHAT YOU'RE SAYING?!

02:38.829 --> 02:40.331
BECAUSE I AM
THE BELLE OF THIS BALL!

02:40.331 --> 02:43.234
YOU SAID WE WERE BEST FRIENDS
AND I WAS YOUR FAVORITE,

02:43.234 --> 02:45.196
AND GET YOUR HANDS
OFF OF ME!

02:45.196 --> 02:46.497
YOU LIED TO ME!

02:46.497 --> 02:48.699
MAYBE YOU WERE
BETTER OFF ALONE.

02:51.171 --> 02:55.606
MAYBE WE ALL ARE,
DR. MILLER.

02:55.606 --> 02:57.778
Nolan: WELL, THERE'S A LOT
OF NAMES IN THE HOPPER.

02:57.778 --> 03:02.253
ERASE-ON MANOR. THORNEHILL.
THE ROSS SUPREMACY.

03:02.253 --> 03:04.285
EMILY'S
STILL TAKING PICTURES,

03:04.285 --> 03:06.257
BUT AS FAR AS
THE PARTY SIGNAGE GOES,

03:06.257 --> 03:07.918
A "HAPPY MEMORIAL DAY"
WILL DO.

03:07.918 --> 03:09.820
THE HOUSE DOESN'T NEED A NAME,
NOLAN.

03:09.820 --> 03:13.464
SAYS THE GIRL WHO DOESN'T KNOW
WHICH ONE TO USE FOR HERSELF.

03:13.464 --> 03:15.566
I DO.
YOU JUST WON'T ACCEPT IT.

03:15.566 --> 03:18.499
OH, EMS,
I THINK I'VE ACCEPTED A LOT.

03:18.499 --> 03:21.972
LIKE WHEN YOU SAID
YOU WANTED TO BUY THIS HOUSE,

03:21.972 --> 03:23.203
I REDECORATED.

03:23.203 --> 03:25.576
YOU WANTED TO OPEN
THE SEASON HERE,

03:25.576 --> 03:27.238
I'M CO-HOSTING THE PARTY.

03:27.238 --> 03:29.880
I'M JUST HOPING
THAT YOUR SECRET PLAN

03:29.880 --> 03:32.943
IS TO MAKE YOUR DEBUT THERE
AS AMANDA CLARKE.

03:32.943 --> 03:35.416
SORRY. I'M EMILY THORNE,
AND IT'S SIMPLY A PARTY.

03:35.416 --> 03:37.488
AFTER WHAT THE GRAYSONS
PUT US THROUGH,

03:37.488 --> 03:38.989
DON'T YOU THINK
WE DESERVE ONE?

03:38.989 --> 03:42.623
SO THERE WON'T BE
 ANY POISONINGS?

03:42.623 --> 03:43.924
'FRAID NOT.

03:43.924 --> 03:45.726
NO ARRESTS
OR BLACKMAILINGS?

03:45.726 --> 03:46.997
NOPE.

03:46.997 --> 03:49.330
NO TAKEDOWNS WHATSOEVER?

03:49.330 --> 03:50.901
CONRAD'S DEAD,
I COMMITTED VICTORIA,

03:50.901 --> 03:53.264
AND DANIEL'S SELF-DESTRUCTING
ALL ON HIS OWN.

03:53.264 --> 03:54.935
SO, UNLESS YOU CAN THINK
OF SOMEONE --

03:54.935 --> 03:58.269
NOPE. I CAN'T.
DON'T WANT TO.

03:58.269 --> 04:00.471
THEN STOP QUESTIONING ME,
AND LET'S ENJOY THE SUMMER.

04:00.471 --> 04:03.574
HEY, EMS,
KNOW WHAT THEY SAID

04:03.574 --> 04:05.616
ABOUT THE GIRL
WHO GAVE UP REVENGE?

04:06.917 --> 04:10.281
SHE LIVED
HAPPILY EVER AFTER.

04:18.389 --> 04:20.991
[ DOOR OPENS ]

04:20.991 --> 04:24.435
GOING SOMEWHERE?

04:24.435 --> 04:26.266
YEAH.

04:26.266 --> 04:27.668
I WAS JUST ABOUT
TO COME FIND YOU.

04:27.668 --> 04:29.970
IT'S TIME.

04:29.970 --> 04:32.303
YOU SURE?

04:34.905 --> 04:38.008
[ SIGHS ]
IT'S NOW OR NEVER.

04:38.008 --> 04:40.851
SOMEDAY I WILL REPAY YOU.

04:41.882 --> 04:43.854
BUT WHERE
ARE YOU GONNA GO?

04:45.916 --> 04:49.320
SOUTHAMPTON.

04:49.320 --> 04:51.322
I GOT
SOME UNFINISHED BUSINESS.

05:04.735 --> 05:06.977
[ ENGINE REVVING ]

05:10.411 --> 05:13.644
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

05:13.644 --> 05:15.916
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ]

05:22.423 --> 05:24.925
I'LL BE SENDING YOU THE BILL
FOR HER OVERTIME.

05:24.925 --> 05:25.996
YEAH, PLEASE DO.

05:25.996 --> 05:28.459
PENTHOUSE "B"
AT THE RIPLEY.

05:28.459 --> 05:31.001
OH, YOU LIVE
IN A LUXURY HOTEL NOW?

05:31.001 --> 05:32.332
DOING WHAT YOU CAN

05:32.332 --> 05:35.065
TO TRY AND SALVAGE
THE GRAYSON LIFESTYLE.

05:35.065 --> 05:37.908
YOU'VE CERTAINLY PROFITED
FROM MY FAMILY'S DOWNFALL.

05:37.908 --> 05:40.010
YOU EXPECT ME
TO PROTECT YOUR REPUTATION

05:40.010 --> 05:41.372
AFTER WHAT YOU DID?

05:41.372 --> 05:44.114
I MADE YOU MY SECOND-IN-COMMAND,
MY PARTNER,

05:44.114 --> 05:46.417
BUT THEN YOU QUIT
WITH NO WARNING

05:46.417 --> 05:47.748
AND STILL NO EXPLANATION.

05:49.349 --> 05:53.023
YEAH. YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY ONE
ENDURING FAMILY TRAGEDIES.

05:53.023 --> 05:54.955
WELL, THEN, YOU SHOULD BE
FIGHTING TO REBUILD YOUR LIFE

05:54.955 --> 05:56.627
INSTEAD OF FEEDING
YOUR LIBIDO.

05:56.627 --> 05:58.489
OH, NOW I'M SUPPOSED TO TAKE
YOUR ADVICE?

05:58.489 --> 06:01.792
SAVE YOUR CONCERN
FOR YOUR BROTHER.

06:01.792 --> 06:03.734
OH, I CAN HANDLE HIM.

06:03.734 --> 06:07.698
AT LEAST WITH GIDEON,
THERE ARE NO SURPRISES.

06:07.698 --> 06:10.941
[ ENGINE REVS ]

06:10.941 --> 06:13.003
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT.

06:13.003 --> 06:15.876
AND YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO BUY US DRINKS TONIGHT.

06:15.876 --> 06:17.678
PRECINCT RULES --
ROOKIE PAYS.

06:17.678 --> 06:19.379
HEY,
QUIT HAZING MY PROBIE.

06:19.379 --> 06:21.812
DON'T WORRY, PORTER.
KELLER'S A CHEAP DATE.

06:21.812 --> 06:23.814
ONE BEER
AND HE'S UNDER THE TABLE.

06:23.814 --> 06:26.016
YOU SHOULD TALK, HUNTER.

06:28.018 --> 06:29.960
SO, YOU WANT TO GO
THROW BACK A FEW?

06:29.960 --> 06:30.991
HUH? ON ME?

06:30.991 --> 06:33.023
UH, I CAN'T.

06:33.023 --> 06:34.865
I GOT TO PICK CARL UP
FROM DAYCARE

06:34.865 --> 06:36.597
AND DON'T HAVE
A SITTER TONIGHT.

06:36.597 --> 06:37.668
I HEAR THAT.

06:37.668 --> 06:39.069
I WAS RAISED
BY A SINGLE DAD.

06:39.069 --> 06:41.001
YEAH, A LOT OF GRILLED CHEESE
FOR BREAKFAST,

06:41.001 --> 06:42.803
PANCAKES FOR DINNER.

06:42.803 --> 06:44.875
SO, FIRST DAY OUT THERE.
HOW'D YOU FEEL?

06:44.875 --> 06:46.477
GREEN AS HELL.

06:46.477 --> 06:47.938
HOPE I DIDN'T
MAKE YOU NERVOUS.

06:47.938 --> 06:50.811
WHAT, ON OUR THREE TRAFFIC STOPS
AND ONE DOMESTIC? NO.

06:50.811 --> 06:54.545
JUST REMEMBER TWO THINGS,
ALL RIGHT?

06:54.545 --> 06:57.818
WHY YOU BECAME A COP
AND THAT I GOT YOUR BACK.

06:59.920 --> 07:02.052
WHY DID YOU BECOME A COP?

07:02.052 --> 07:05.956
WELL,
THE BAR IS DOING OKAY

07:05.956 --> 07:08.098
BUT NOT ENOUGH
FOR A COLLEGE FUND.

07:08.098 --> 07:12.733
I GUESS I THOUGHT THIS WOULD BE
GOOD FOR THE SOUL.

07:12.733 --> 07:17.938
I'VE JUST SEEN TOO MANY PEOPLE
GET AWAY WITH MURDER AND...

07:17.938 --> 07:20.771
I FINALLY WANTED THE POWER
TO DO SOMETHING ABOUT IT.

07:20.771 --> 07:21.972
REALLY?

07:21.972 --> 07:23.744
SO YOU AREN'T DOING THIS
SO THAT YOU CAN START

07:23.744 --> 07:26.076
ARRESTING PEOPLE
INSTEAD OF KIDNAPPING THEM?

07:26.076 --> 07:29.219
NEVER GONNA LIVE THAT DOWN,
AM I?

07:29.219 --> 07:30.721
NO.
NO, YOU GOT TO OWN IT.

07:30.721 --> 07:32.523
I MEAN,
HOW MANY OF US CAN ACTUALLY SAY

07:32.523 --> 07:34.655
THAT WE'VE BEEN DETAINED
FOR A CLASS "B" FELONY?

07:34.655 --> 07:37.488
[ CHUCKLES ] AMAZING.

07:38.659 --> 07:40.160
♪ ...STRAIGHT,
NEVER CHASE THAT ♪

07:40.160 --> 07:42.863
WELL, MY FITTING WENT
SWIMMINGLY.

07:42.863 --> 07:46.096
MY PARTY OUTFIT IS KIND OF EPIC,
EVEN FOR ME.

07:46.096 --> 07:49.139
ARE WE PLAYING
MUSICAL CHAIRS?

07:49.139 --> 07:50.801
I FIGURED
I'D DRIVE US HOME.

07:50.801 --> 07:51.972
EMS, I TOLD YOU.

07:51.972 --> 07:54.144
I HAD THIS LITTLE MINX
CUSTOM-MADE

07:54.144 --> 07:55.846
FOR OUR SUMMER OF FUN,

07:55.846 --> 07:59.049
BUT THERE IS ONLY ONE BLOND
ALLOWED BEHIND THE WHEEL.

07:59.049 --> 08:01.612
LOOK, IF YOU WANT ME
TO EMBRACE A NEW LIFE,

08:01.612 --> 08:03.984
THEN MAYBE YOU SHOULD EMBRACE
SOME NEW RULES.

08:03.984 --> 08:05.015
HOP IN.

08:05.015 --> 08:07.257
♪ BLO-O-O-W ♪

08:07.257 --> 08:10.060
♪ I SAID, "BABY, I DO THIS,"
I THOUGHT THAT YOU KNEW THIS ♪

08:10.060 --> 08:12.963
♪ CAN'T STAND NO HATERS
AND HONEST, THE TRUTH IS ♪

08:12.963 --> 08:14.525
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

08:14.525 --> 08:15.826
♪ THEY SPEAK IT, DEPART IT ♪

08:15.826 --> 08:16.927
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

08:16.927 --> 08:18.068
OH, MY GOD!

08:18.068 --> 08:20.130
Man:
ARE THEY ALL RIGHT?

08:20.130 --> 08:22.102
I'LL BUY YOU A NEW ONE.

08:22.102 --> 08:23.133
HEY!

08:23.133 --> 08:25.035
HEY!

08:25.035 --> 08:27.077
ARE YOU BLIND?!

08:28.709 --> 08:32.111
I AM SO SORRY. I'M NOT USED TO
DRIVING THIS CAR.

08:32.111 --> 08:33.644
UNREAL.

08:33.644 --> 08:36.015
YOU KNOW, EVERY SUMMER,
YOU PEOPLE COME FLOCKING IN HERE

08:36.015 --> 08:37.246
LIKE YOU OWN THIS TOWN.

08:37.246 --> 08:39.149
OH, THIS IS JUST FANTA--
YOU KNOW WHAT?

08:39.149 --> 08:40.721
JUST -- JUST GIVE ME
YOUR INSURANCE.

08:40.721 --> 08:43.123
OH, WE DON'T NEED TO HASSLE
WITH THAT. I'LL JUST COVER IT.

08:43.123 --> 08:44.855
MUST BE NICE
LIVING IN YOUR WORLD.

08:44.855 --> 08:47.197
[ SIGHS ]
JUST BRING ME THE ESTIMATE.

08:47.197 --> 08:50.130
I'M IN THE HOUSE ON
THE EAST EDGE OF COOPERS BEACH.

08:50.130 --> 08:52.803
THE OLD GRAYSON MANNER.

08:52.803 --> 08:54.164
THIS IS WHY
WE NEED A NAME.

08:54.164 --> 08:56.066
OH, YOU'RE EMILY THORNE.

08:56.066 --> 08:57.708
YEAH, I HEARD
YOU BOUGHT THAT PLACE.

08:57.708 --> 08:58.939
BEEN LISTENING TO MY CUSTOMERS

08:58.939 --> 09:00.540
YAPPING ABOUT YOUR PARTY
ALL WEEK.

09:00.540 --> 09:02.172
WELL, WHY DON'T YOU COME?
 [ CHUCKLES ]

09:02.172 --> 09:03.774
BRING THE ESTIMATE THEN,

09:03.774 --> 09:06.076
AND YOU'LL SEE
WE'RE NOT ALL THAT BAD.

09:06.076 --> 09:07.678
YOU KNOW WHAT?

09:07.678 --> 09:09.049
IF THAT'S THE SOONEST I CAN GET
THE CHECK FROM YOU, FINE.

09:09.049 --> 09:11.281
PERFECT. WE'LL SEE YOU THEN.
 YEAH.

09:11.281 --> 09:14.084
AND, AGAIN, I'M SORRY.
 YEAH.

09:14.084 --> 09:18.558
LOOK AT YOU -- SOLVING CONFLICT
WITHOUT A RED SHARPIE.

09:20.731 --> 09:22.262
I'LL DRIVE.

09:26.637 --> 09:28.298
CHARLOTTE!

09:28.298 --> 09:31.101
THERE'S DADDY.
SAY HELLO, CARL.

09:31.101 --> 09:33.103
WHAT THE HELL?

09:33.103 --> 09:35.105
YOU DON'T TALK TO ME
FOR SIX MONTHS

09:35.105 --> 09:38.148
AND THEN OUT OF THE BLUE
YOU PICK HIM UP FROM DAYCARE?

09:38.148 --> 09:40.651
COME HERE.
 I MISSED THE LITTLE GUY.

09:40.651 --> 09:43.083
YOU KNOW WHAT THAT WAS LIKE
FOR ME?

09:43.083 --> 09:45.916
NOT KNOWING WHERE HE IS,
NOT BEING ABLE TO FIND HIM?

09:45.916 --> 09:48.588
AND HOW'S THAT FEEL,
JACK?

09:48.588 --> 09:52.062
THAT FEAR,
THAT KNOT IN YOUR STOMACH?

09:52.062 --> 09:55.595
THOUGHT I'D REMIND YOU
WHO YOU REALLY ARE

09:55.595 --> 09:57.227
AFTER YOUR FIRST DAY
ON THE JOB.

09:57.227 --> 10:00.070
[ CARL CRYING ]
 PROTECT AND SERVE, RIGHT?

10:00.070 --> 10:01.371
THAT'S NOT
WHAT YOU DID FOR ME

10:01.371 --> 10:03.173
WHEN YOU TIED ME UP
IN THAT ROOM.

10:03.173 --> 10:06.637
I TOLD YOU AGAIN AND AGAIN,
IT WASN'T ME.

10:06.637 --> 10:09.039
THEN LOOK ME IN THE EYE
AND SAY IT.

10:09.039 --> 10:12.783
AFTER ALL THIS TIME,
YOU STILL CAN'T, CAN YOU, JACK?

10:12.783 --> 10:14.184
CHARLOTTE, YOU'RE JUST GONNA
HAVE TO LET THIS GO.

10:14.184 --> 10:18.118
CALM DOWN, JACK.
YOU'RE SCARING YOUR SON.

10:18.118 --> 10:20.851
POOR LITTLE GUY --

10:20.851 --> 10:23.353
BEING RAISED
BY A DIRTY COP.

10:23.353 --> 10:26.156
[ CRYING ]

10:34.004 --> 10:36.106
I HAD A PREMONITION.

10:36.106 --> 10:39.069
IT'S GOING TO RAIN.

10:39.069 --> 10:41.972
"IT'S GOING TO RAIN AGAIN.

10:41.972 --> 10:45.145
"RAIN EVERY DAY,
AS THOUGH TO SPITE ME.

10:45.145 --> 10:47.678
I MIGHT AS WELL
HANG MYSELF."

10:52.783 --> 10:54.354
IT'S CHEKHOV.

10:54.354 --> 10:59.029
I LIKE IT.
ESPECIALLY THE END.

11:04.094 --> 11:06.266
[ SIGHS ]

11:09.840 --> 11:11.742
It worked.

11:19.409 --> 11:22.282
How did you know the orderly
would have it on him?

11:22.282 --> 11:24.985
Because his wife is due
in two weeks,

11:24.985 --> 11:26.286
which is when men think

11:26.286 --> 11:29.019
they're suddenly vital
to the process.

11:29.019 --> 11:33.223
I haven't had that much fun
in years...

11:33.223 --> 11:35.065
without acid.

11:35.065 --> 11:37.968
Phyllis, thank you.

11:42.803 --> 11:44.004
[ GLASSES CLINK ]
 Dennis: CHEERS.

11:44.004 --> 11:46.206
THE LONG ISLAND
HARBOR CONSERVANCY

11:46.206 --> 11:48.038
APPRECIATES YOUR FUNDRAISING
EFFORTS, MS. THORNE.

11:48.038 --> 11:50.811
OH, WELL, I COULDN'T IMAGINE
A BETTER EVENT

11:50.811 --> 11:54.214
TO BREAK IN MY NEW HOME OR
CHRISTEN YOUR NEW YACHT, DENNIS.

11:54.214 --> 11:56.016
SHE LOOKS LIKE
A BEAUTY.

11:56.016 --> 11:57.217
WELL, SHE IS --

11:57.217 --> 11:59.489
JUST AS BEAUTIFUL
AS THE WOMAN I NAMED IT FOR.

11:59.489 --> 12:00.951
[ CHUCKLES ]
 OH.

12:00.951 --> 12:02.322
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
HOW EMBARRASSING IT IS

12:02.322 --> 12:04.154
TO HAVE YOUR NAME PAINTED
ON THE SIDE OF A BOAT.

12:05.455 --> 12:07.227
I THINK IT'S AN HONOR.

12:07.227 --> 12:10.000
FORTUNATELY, YOU HAVE
A LOVELY NAME LIKE JENNIFER.

12:10.000 --> 12:11.201
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:11.201 --> 12:13.363
SO, WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR LAST YACHT?

12:13.363 --> 12:16.106
I'M SURPRISED
YOU HADN'T HEARD.

12:16.106 --> 12:19.770
IT WAS INVOLVED
IN AN ACCIDENT LAST SUMMER

12:19.770 --> 12:22.012
WITH A SMALL FISHING BOAT.

12:22.012 --> 12:23.373
A MAN WAS KILLED.

12:23.373 --> 12:26.016
OH, YES, I REMEMBER.

12:26.016 --> 12:29.019
BUT YOUR SKIPPER TOOK IT OUT
FOR A JOYRIDE, RIGHT?

12:29.019 --> 12:30.120
THAT'S RIGHT, YEAH.

12:30.120 --> 12:32.152
IT'S JUST SO HORRIBLE
TO THINK ABOUT.

12:32.152 --> 12:33.153
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]

12:33.153 --> 12:36.026
EXCUSE ME.

12:41.832 --> 12:44.094
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

12:44.094 --> 12:45.495
[ TELEPHONE BEEPS ]

12:45.495 --> 12:46.766
HELLO?

12:46.766 --> 12:48.238
VICTORIA:
This is Victoria Grayson.

12:48.238 --> 12:49.970
I'm being held captive
at Claremont Institu--

12:49.970 --> 12:51.441
I KNOW EXACTLY WHERE YOU ARE,
VICTORIA.

12:51.441 --> 12:55.345
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
IN MY HOUSE?

12:55.345 --> 12:58.378
I'M PAYING THE MORTGAGE.

12:58.378 --> 13:00.250
YOU SHOULD SEE
WHAT I'VE DONE WITH THE PLACE.

13:00.250 --> 13:03.253
I changed everything
except the phone number,

13:03.253 --> 13:04.815
A PRECAUTION
I'M SURE YOU NOW UNDERSTAND.

13:04.815 --> 13:06.817
PLEASE.

13:06.817 --> 13:09.089
I'VE HURT YOU. I ADMIT IT.

13:09.089 --> 13:11.391
BUT YOU'VE HURT ME, TOO.

13:11.391 --> 13:15.125
I JUST WANT TO END THIS CYCLE,
PLEASE.

13:15.125 --> 13:17.567
AND I WANT MY CHILDHOOD.

13:17.567 --> 13:19.099
I WANT AIDEN.

13:19.099 --> 13:21.371
AND I WANT PASCAL BACK.

13:21.371 --> 13:23.974
YOU LED HIM TO HIS DEATH.

13:23.974 --> 13:27.537
You insinuated
your way into my family.

13:27.537 --> 13:29.509
YOU HAVE EARNED YOUR PAIN.

13:29.509 --> 13:31.942
YOU ARE EXACTLY
WHERE YOU BELONG, VICTORIA,

13:31.942 --> 13:33.183
RANTING ON LIKE A LUNATIC.

13:33.183 --> 13:35.846
FOR THE RECORD, CONRAD
SLAUGHTERED PASCAL, NOT ME.

13:35.846 --> 13:37.948
And as for everything else
I did...

13:37.948 --> 13:39.890
I WOULD DO IT ALL AGAIN.

13:39.890 --> 13:42.052
SORRY YOU WASTED YOUR CALL.

14:03.043 --> 14:04.414
HEY.

14:04.414 --> 14:07.117
HEY.

14:07.117 --> 14:08.248
NOLAN WAS WRONG.

14:08.248 --> 14:09.920
YOU DON'T LOOK ANYTHING
LIKE A STRIPPER.

14:09.920 --> 14:11.882
[ SCOFFS ]

14:11.882 --> 14:15.485
JACK, YOU DON'T NEED TO KEEP
COMING OVER TO CHECK IN ON ME.

14:15.485 --> 14:17.187
I'M FINE.
 I'M NOT.

14:17.187 --> 14:18.889
CHARLOTTE TOOK CARL
FROM DAYCARE.

14:18.889 --> 14:20.891
WHAT?
 HE'S FINE.

14:20.891 --> 14:25.065
SHE JUST -- SHE JUST DID IT
TO SCARE ME, AND IT WORKED.

14:25.065 --> 14:30.200
MY, UH -- MY PARTNER ASKED ME
TODAY WHY I BECAME A COP.

14:30.200 --> 14:35.105
HE JOKED THAT IT HAD SOMETHING
TO DO WITH THE KIDNAPPING.

14:35.105 --> 14:37.077
WELL, HE WAS RIGHT,
WASN'T HE?

14:37.077 --> 14:39.980
[ SIGHS ] WELL...

14:39.980 --> 14:42.052
IT'S A LITTLE MORE COMPLICATED
THAN THAT.

14:45.055 --> 14:50.220
I FIRST THOUGHT ABOUT
JOINING THE FORCE

14:50.220 --> 14:55.895
AFTER, UH,
AMANDA'S MURDER

14:55.895 --> 14:59.599
AND AGAIN
AFTER MY BROTHER WAS KILLED.

14:59.599 --> 15:02.132
I HATED THE POWERLESSNESS,

15:02.132 --> 15:06.476
'CAUSE I KNEW THAT CONRAD
HAD THE COPS IN HIS POCKET.

15:06.476 --> 15:12.242
I KNEW THAT IF I BECAME A COP,
NO ONE COULD PAY ME OFF.

15:12.242 --> 15:15.215
SO WHY DIDN'T YOU JOIN
BACK THEN?

15:15.215 --> 15:17.117
BECAUSE I LEARNED
WHO YOU WERE.

15:17.117 --> 15:21.651
LISTEN, AT THE ACADEMY,
THEY DRUM INTO US THIS IDEA

15:21.651 --> 15:23.994
THAT WE'RE WORKING
FOR THE GREATER GOOD.

15:23.994 --> 15:27.998
AND I KNOW THAT THAT'S WHAT YOU
WERE DOING IN YOUR OWN WAY,

15:27.998 --> 15:30.500
BUT YOU KNOW
I WAS NEVER OKAY WITH THAT.

15:30.500 --> 15:32.532
YOU WERE WAITING FOR ME
TO BE DONE.

15:35.265 --> 15:38.668
JACK, YOU DIDN'T HAVE TO PUT
YOUR LIFE ON HOLD TO PROTECT ME.

15:38.668 --> 15:42.072
WELL, I'M JUST GLAD
THAT IT'S OVER...

15:43.573 --> 15:45.445
...THAT YOU'RE MOVING ON.

15:47.277 --> 15:48.478
Man: MA'AM?

15:48.478 --> 15:50.981
WE'RE READY.
 UM, I'LL BE RIGHT WITH YOU.

15:50.981 --> 15:52.582
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

15:54.484 --> 15:57.527
AND, LOOK, IN CASE THERE WAS
EVER ANY DOUBT

15:57.527 --> 16:00.590
AS TO WHY I STAYED
IN THE HAMPTONS,

16:00.590 --> 16:02.362
IT WAS FOR CHARLOTTE.

16:04.464 --> 16:06.236
SHE'S THE ONLY FAMILY
I HAVE,

16:06.236 --> 16:09.099
AND ONE WAY OR ANOTHER,
I WILL MAKE IT BETTER.

16:20.650 --> 16:22.652
SO, YOU HEARD FROM MOM?

16:22.652 --> 16:24.684
YEAH, THE POSTCARDS
STOPPED COMING.

16:24.684 --> 16:26.756
LAST ONE SAID
SHE WAS IN AMSTERDAM.

16:26.756 --> 16:29.559
I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE
SHE DITCHED US TO SAVE HERSELF.

16:29.559 --> 16:31.021
[ CHUCKLES ] CAN'T YOU?

16:31.021 --> 16:33.063
WHEN THE GOVERNMENT
TOOK EVERYTHING,

16:33.063 --> 16:35.065
SHE WAS THE FIRST RAT
OFF THE SHIP.

16:35.065 --> 16:38.398
WELL, AT LEAST YOU STILL HAVE
THE MONEY YOU MADE AT LeMARCHAL.

16:38.398 --> 16:42.772
SPEAKING OF, WOULD YOU MIND
COVERING MY RENT AGAIN?

16:42.772 --> 16:46.436
[ Chuckling ]
CHAR, WE TALKED ABOUT THIS.

16:46.436 --> 16:48.708
YOU KNOW I DON'T LOVE
YOU LIVING ALONE DOWNTOWN.

16:48.708 --> 16:51.611
WHY DON'T YOU MOVE IN
WITH ME?

16:51.611 --> 16:54.084
YOU JUST WANT TO KEEP ME
UNDER YOUR THUMB.

16:54.084 --> 16:55.215
YEAH, YOU'RE RIGHT.
I DO.

16:55.215 --> 16:58.248
I BARELY HEAR FROM YOU,
AND I-I WORRY.

16:58.248 --> 17:01.291
WITH WHAT YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH,
YOU NEED A SUPPORT SYSTEM.

17:01.291 --> 17:03.423
I'M DOING FINE, THANKS.

17:03.423 --> 17:07.297
WELL, THEN, DO FINE HERE
WITH YOUR BROTHER.

17:07.297 --> 17:10.230
IT'S NO GRAYSON MANNER,
BUT...

17:10.230 --> 17:12.232
YEAH, YOU KNOW,
EMILY'S THROWING

17:12.232 --> 17:14.064
HER MEMORIAL DAY PARTY THERE
TOMORROW.

17:14.064 --> 17:16.205
SHE EVEN HAD THE GALL
TO INVITE ME.

17:16.205 --> 17:17.467
[ SCOFFS ]

17:17.467 --> 17:19.309
WELL, THAT BITCH NEVER KNOWS
WHEN TO QUIT, DOES SHE?

17:19.309 --> 17:20.810
YEAH, NEITHER DO I.

17:20.810 --> 17:23.272
NOW,
HOW ABOUT THAT RENT CHECK?

17:23.272 --> 17:25.675
MM.

17:25.675 --> 17:27.117
UM...

17:27.117 --> 17:29.679
YEAH, HOW -- HOW --
HOW MUCH WAS IT AGAIN?

17:29.679 --> 17:30.820
FIVE GRAND?

17:30.820 --> 17:32.482
SEVEN.

17:32.482 --> 17:33.753
SEVEN GRAND?

17:33.753 --> 17:35.325
IS THAT OKAY?

17:35.325 --> 17:37.257
ANYTHING
FOR MY LITTLE SISTER.

17:43.463 --> 17:47.197
[ CRYING ]

17:57.477 --> 18:00.510
HOPE YOU DON'T MIND
THEY PUT ME IN HERE.

18:00.510 --> 18:01.851
NOT AS LONG
AS YOU STOP CRYING.

18:01.851 --> 18:04.714
THIS PLACE DOESN'T DESERVE
YOUR TEARS.

18:04.714 --> 18:07.157
[ SIGHS ]

18:07.157 --> 18:10.089
I'M LOUISE --
LOUISE ELLIS.

18:10.089 --> 18:12.091
VICTORIA GRAYSON.

18:12.091 --> 18:14.494
AS IN CONRAD GRAYSON?

18:14.494 --> 18:16.396
MM-HMM.

18:16.396 --> 18:18.528
I'M SORRY FOR YOUR LOSS.

18:18.528 --> 18:20.170
I'M NOT.

18:20.170 --> 18:23.533
THAT MAN WAS A TYRANT.

18:23.533 --> 18:27.677
I SEE
THAT YOU'VE OVERPACKED.

18:27.677 --> 18:29.679
MOTHER SAID
SHE WAS SENDING ME

18:29.679 --> 18:31.641
TO A HEALTH SPA
TO REJUVENATE.

18:31.641 --> 18:35.485
IF YOU'RE WORRIED THAT I MIGHT
CUT YOU IN YOUR SLEEP,

18:35.485 --> 18:36.646
I'M NOT CRAZY.

18:36.646 --> 18:39.289
AW, THAT'S TOO BAD.

18:39.289 --> 18:42.192
SANITY'S YOUR ENEMY HERE.

18:42.192 --> 18:48.258
I SPUN OUT A BIT [SIGHS]
AFTER MY DADDY DIED LAST YEAR.

18:48.258 --> 18:51.201
HE DRANK HIMSELF TO DEATH.

18:51.201 --> 18:56.736
MY MOM'S BEEN TRYING TO CONVINCE
ME I'M STILL SCREWED UP,

18:56.736 --> 19:00.770
THAT I NEED TIME
TO FIGURE THINGS OUT.

19:00.770 --> 19:05.144
I CAN'T IMAGINE
CHOOSING THIS FOR YOUR CHILD.

19:05.144 --> 19:07.877
WELL, THEN, YOU'RE
A BETTER MOTHER THAN MINE.

19:10.920 --> 19:15.255
WELL, YOU'LL SOON LEARN
THAT THIS PLACE IS A PRISON,

19:15.255 --> 19:18.658
AND DR. MILLER
IS ITS WELL-PAID WARDEN.

19:18.658 --> 19:21.761
TOOK ME SIX MONTHS
JUST TO OBTAIN A PHONE.

19:21.761 --> 19:24.634
BUT YOU DID CALL SOMEBODY,
DIDN'T YOU?

19:24.634 --> 19:27.437
SADLY, I REACHED THE VERY DEVIL
WHO COMMITTED ME.

19:27.437 --> 19:31.571
WELL, YOU MUST KNOW
ANOTHER WAY OUT.

19:31.571 --> 19:33.303
PLEASE.

19:33.303 --> 19:35.275
I WILL LOSE IT IN HERE,

19:35.275 --> 19:38.648
WHICH I'M SURE IS EXACTLY
WHAT MY MOTHER WANTS.

19:38.648 --> 19:41.381
POOR POPPET.

19:43.653 --> 19:46.856
ENJOY THE TRAPPINGS
OF YOUR FORMER LIFE

19:46.856 --> 19:48.958
WHILE YOU STILL HAVE THEM,

19:48.958 --> 19:51.561
BECAUSE THEY TAKE EVERYTHING
AWAY FROM YOU HERE.

19:51.561 --> 19:54.924
[ WHIMPERS ]

20:00.300 --> 20:02.702
MAYBE WE SHOULD LET THEM.

20:19.919 --> 20:23.753
YOU BETTER NOT
DISAPPEAR ON ME AGAIN.

20:23.753 --> 20:26.256
Aiden: I WON'T, AMANDA.

20:38.908 --> 20:40.970
[ LOCK CLICKS ]

20:59.829 --> 21:03.293
AIDEN?

21:04.934 --> 21:06.936
NO.

21:06.936 --> 21:07.937
NO!

21:16.906 --> 21:19.409
[ SIGHS ]

21:40.069 --> 21:44.073
♪ NO, I, I CAN'T FEEL THE HEAT ♪

21:44.073 --> 21:48.037
♪ YET DON'T LET IT CATCH YOU ♪

21:48.037 --> 21:54.484
♪ NO, I, I CAN'T FEEL THE HEAT ♪

21:54.484 --> 21:57.487
♪ I KNOW I CAN'T GET YOU HOME ♪

21:57.487 --> 22:00.490
OKAY. GO AHEAD.
 ♪ NO, I CAN'T FINISH
MY WORKOUT ♪

22:00.490 --> 22:01.951
HI.
 HI.

22:07.597 --> 22:11.000
♪ I KNEW THAT THE MOMENT I RUN,
HONEY ♪

22:11.000 --> 22:12.932
YOU MADE IT.

22:12.932 --> 22:14.103
YEAH. [ CHUCKLES ]

22:14.103 --> 22:16.065
YEAH.

22:16.065 --> 22:17.867
THIS CHECK IS FOR YOU.

22:19.108 --> 22:22.071
THAT'S -- IT'S TOO MUCH.
I MEAN, THE ESTIMATE'S ONLY --

22:22.071 --> 22:23.913
PLEASE, PLEASE.
TO COVER THE HASSLE.

22:23.913 --> 22:26.115
THANK YOU.

22:27.477 --> 22:32.522
LOOK, UM, I'M SORRY I BLEW UP
AT YOU THE OTHER DAY.

22:32.522 --> 22:35.955
JUST -- JUST BEEN A REALLY
CRAPPY YEAR, YOU KNOW.

22:35.955 --> 22:39.489
AND I GUESS I JUST --
I-I EXPECT THE WORST OF PEOPLE.

22:39.489 --> 22:41.130
OH, BELIEVE ME,
I'VE BEEN THERE.

22:41.130 --> 22:44.464
NOT SO SURE YOU HAVE.

22:44.464 --> 22:49.969
JUST HAD A REALLY SHORT FUSE
EVER SINCE I LOST MY FIANCé.

22:49.969 --> 22:52.602
WOW. [ CHUCKLES ]

22:52.602 --> 22:53.973
TOO MUCH TOO SOON,
I KNOW.

22:53.973 --> 22:55.705
NO, NO. NOT AT ALL.

22:57.507 --> 22:59.108
I LOST SOMEONE, TOO.

22:59.108 --> 23:01.951
AND TO BE COMPLETELY HONEST,
IT'S BEEN HARD

23:01.951 --> 23:04.954
TO FIND SOMEONE WHO UNDERSTANDS
WHAT I WENT THROUGH. SO...

23:07.517 --> 23:10.159
I'M GLAD YOU CAME, NANCY.
WOULD YOU STAY?

23:10.159 --> 23:12.091
YEAH.

23:12.091 --> 23:14.023
[ FANFARE PLAYS ]

23:14.023 --> 23:17.927
EVERY QUEEN OF THE HAMPTONS
NEEDS HER THRONE.

23:19.469 --> 23:24.974
AND THIS ONE EVEN HAS ROOM
FOR HER JESTER.

23:24.974 --> 23:25.905
YOU LIKE?

23:26.936 --> 23:28.077
I LOVE.

23:30.109 --> 23:34.013
LONG LIVE THE NEW QUEEN.

23:34.013 --> 23:36.085
Crowd: CHEERS!
 Charlotte: LOOK AT HER,

23:36.085 --> 23:38.117
RUBBING MY NOSE IN EVERYTHING
THAT'S HAPPENED.

23:38.117 --> 23:40.049
WHY DON'T WE JUST
RUB OUR NOSES

23:40.049 --> 23:42.021
INTO SOMETHING
A LITTLE BIT MORE FUN?

23:43.893 --> 23:46.896
RIGHT AFTER I SAY HI
TO THE HOSTESS.

23:46.896 --> 23:48.157
OKAY.

23:49.729 --> 23:52.702
[ SIGHS ]
THANK YOU FOR COMING, CHARLOTTE.

23:52.702 --> 23:54.033
I ONLY ACCEPTED YOUR INVITE

23:54.033 --> 23:56.466
BECAUSE I THOUGHT
AFTER ALL THIS TIME,

23:56.466 --> 23:58.067
MAYBE YOU'D SURPRISE ME,

23:58.067 --> 23:59.909
BUT MY MOM WAS RIGHT,
WASN'T SHE?

23:59.909 --> 24:03.172
THIS IS ALL YOU EVER WANTED --
THIS LIFESTYLE, THIS HOUSE.

24:03.172 --> 24:05.745
I WISH YOU'D GIVE ME
A CHANCE TO EXPLAIN.

24:05.745 --> 24:07.116
WHY WOULD I GIVE YOU ANYTHING,
EMILY?

24:07.116 --> 24:08.978
WHEN YOU WANT SOMETHING,
YOU JUST TAKE IT.

24:13.583 --> 24:14.954
Man: WANTED ONE OF THESE

24:14.954 --> 24:17.226
EVER SINCE I SAW "GOLDFINGER"
AS A KID.

24:17.226 --> 24:18.988
SO WHY ARE YOU
LETTING HER GO?

24:18.988 --> 24:20.089
OH, I DON'T KNOW.

24:20.089 --> 24:22.161
I GUESS I REALIZED
SOME THINGS IN LIFE

24:22.161 --> 24:25.965
WERE MORE IMPORTANT THAN
PRETENDING TO BE JAMES BOND.

24:25.965 --> 24:27.567
REALLY?

24:27.567 --> 24:31.470
RUMOR IS YOU'VE BEEN SELLING
ANYTHING THAT'S NOT NAILED DOWN

24:31.470 --> 24:33.102
SO YOU CAN KEEP PRETENDING
YOUR FORTUNE DIDN'T SINK

24:33.102 --> 24:34.974
ALONG WITH YOUR FAMILY'S.

24:34.974 --> 24:38.848
IF YOU THINK YOU KNOW SO MUCH,
THEN WHY THE HELL DID YOU ASK?

24:45.755 --> 24:47.657
WE AGREED
TO A LOT MORE THAN THIS.

24:47.657 --> 24:49.519
SUPPLY AND DEMAND,
GRAYSON,

24:49.519 --> 24:53.022
AND YOUR NAME DOESN'T INTIMIDATE
PEOPLE THE WAY IT USED TO.

24:53.022 --> 24:55.494
SO WHY DON'T YOU JUST
HAND ME THE KEYS?

24:55.494 --> 24:57.967
LISTEN TO ME,
YOU SON OF A BITCH,

24:57.967 --> 24:59.769
IF I READ ABOUT THIS SALE
IN "PAGE SIX"

24:59.769 --> 25:01.871
OR IN YOUR FAMILY CHRISTMAS
NEWS LETTER,

25:01.871 --> 25:04.003
YOU'LL SEE JUST HOW INTIMIDATING
I CAN BE.

25:04.003 --> 25:07.136
NOW GET OUT OF HERE.

25:09.979 --> 25:11.280
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

25:20.149 --> 25:21.951
♪ HOW COULD YOU KNOW ♪

25:21.951 --> 25:25.955
♪ HOW COULD YOU KNOW
THAT THOSE WERE MY EYES ♪

25:25.955 --> 25:28.558
♪ PEEPIN' THROUGH THE FLOOR ♪

25:28.558 --> 25:30.159
♪ IT'S LIKE THEY KNOW... ♪

25:30.159 --> 25:32.131
JENNIFER?

25:32.131 --> 25:34.163
YOU ALL RIGHT?

25:34.163 --> 25:37.066
NERVOUS, I GUESS.

25:37.066 --> 25:38.638
I'VE NEVER CHRISTENED
A BOAT BEFORE.

25:38.638 --> 25:40.139
[ CHUCKLES ] OH.
WELL, DON'T WORRY.
 Woman: CHAMPAGNE?

25:40.139 --> 25:41.140
IT WON'T FEEL A THING.

25:41.140 --> 25:43.312
AH, THANK YOU.
 CHEERS.

25:43.312 --> 25:45.174
CHEERS.

25:45.174 --> 25:47.316
♪ ...TO TAKE ME TO THE CLUB
BECAUSE THEY KNOW... ♪

25:47.316 --> 25:49.178
MARGAUX.

25:49.178 --> 25:52.922
UM, I WANTED TO SAY THANK YOU
FOR THE DONATION

25:52.922 --> 25:54.984
AND FOR ACCEPTING
MY INVITATION.

25:54.984 --> 25:56.956
SINCE I'M COVERING
THE SUMMER PARTIES

25:56.956 --> 25:59.829
AND NOW YOU'RE THE ONE THROWING
THEM, IT SEEMED NECESSARY.

25:59.829 --> 26:02.031
AND I WAS CURIOUS TO SEE

26:02.031 --> 26:04.834
HOW YOU WOULD ERASE VICTORIA
FROM HERE.

26:04.834 --> 26:07.136
[ CHUCKLES ]
 THOROUGHLY, IT SEEMS.

26:07.136 --> 26:10.169
WELL, I LIKE TO FORGET
AS MUCH OF MY PAST AS POSSIBLE.

26:10.169 --> 26:11.771
MY NEW MANTRA.

26:11.771 --> 26:15.875
I REGRET LETTING DANIEL COLOR
MY EARLIER OPINION OF YOU.

26:15.875 --> 26:19.048
WELL, WE'VE BOTH BEEN BURNED
BY THAT MATCH.

26:19.048 --> 26:21.050
BUT I LIKE TO THINK
HE'S GETTING HIS

26:21.050 --> 26:23.182
NOW THAT HE'S THE SON OF
THE MOST HATED MAN IN AMERICA.

26:25.785 --> 26:29.118
FEEL LIKE I DIED
AND WENT TO BILLY JOEL'S HOUSE.
 CHAMPAGNE?

26:29.118 --> 26:30.219
AH, THAT'S FUNNY.

26:30.219 --> 26:33.122
FEEL LIKE
I'M IN "THE TWILIGHT ZONE."

26:33.122 --> 26:35.024
PORTER, I MEAN,
YOU'VE GOT TO BE

26:35.024 --> 26:37.667
THE MOST CONNECTED ROOKIE
THAT I'VE EVER KNOWN.

26:37.667 --> 26:39.729
WHO'S YOUR IN HERE?

26:39.729 --> 26:41.831
SHE'S OVER THERE.

26:41.831 --> 26:43.873
EMILY THORNE.

26:43.873 --> 26:45.705
YEAH?

26:45.705 --> 26:48.037
YOU TWO GOT A LITTLE SOMETHING
GOING ON?

26:48.037 --> 26:51.040
NO, UH, IT'S COMPLICATED.

26:51.040 --> 26:54.083
YEAH, WELL UNCOMPLICATE IT.
SHE'S HOT.

26:54.083 --> 26:56.986
♪ ...YOU UNDERSTAND,
THEY GOT A PLAN FOR US... ♪

26:56.986 --> 26:58.017
HER, TOO?

26:58.017 --> 27:00.149
COME ON,
AS YOUR COMMANDING OFFICER,

27:00.149 --> 27:02.652
I ORDER YOU
TO TELL ME YOUR SECRET.

27:02.652 --> 27:04.093
[ LAUGHS ]
COME ON.

27:04.093 --> 27:06.255
I'LL SHOW YOU
THE REST OF THE PLACE.

27:06.255 --> 27:08.327
♪ ...I BET YOU DIDN'T KNOW ♪

27:08.327 --> 27:09.729
♪ SOMEONE COULD
LOVE YOU THIS MUCH... ♪

27:09.729 --> 27:11.030
GAME'S IN PROGRESS, GUYS.
SORRY.

27:11.030 --> 27:13.332
CHARLOTTE,
YOU'RE STRIPES, BABE.

27:13.332 --> 27:14.964
I'LL BE RIGHT THERE.

27:18.367 --> 27:20.169
YOU GUYS WANT A BUMP?

27:20.169 --> 27:21.711
NO, I THINK I'LL PASS.

27:21.711 --> 27:23.142
MISS, STEP BACK AND PUT YOUR
HANDS ON YOUR HEAD, PLEASE.

27:23.142 --> 27:24.313
YOU CAN'T BE SERIOUS.

27:24.313 --> 27:25.945
BEN, BEN,
LET ME HANDLE THIS.

27:25.945 --> 27:26.976
LOOK,
GIVEN YOUR HISTORY WITH HER,

27:26.976 --> 27:27.977
I THINK YOU NEED
TO STEP BACK, TOO.

27:27.977 --> 27:28.978
HEY, YOU STAY RIGHT THERE.

27:28.978 --> 27:30.019
LOOK,
WE CAN'T DO THIS TO HER.

27:30.019 --> 27:31.420
SHE'S NOT IN A GOOD PLACE
RIGHT NOW.

27:31.420 --> 27:34.183
WORD OF ADVICE, PORTER,
YOUR DUTY IS TO PROTECT.

27:34.183 --> 27:37.827
YOU CAN'T LOOK OUT FOR PEOPLE
IF YOU'RE LOOKING THE OTHER WAY.

27:37.827 --> 27:39.058
SHE'S FAMILY.

27:41.130 --> 27:44.163
FINE.

27:44.163 --> 27:46.295
BUT YOU GET ONE PASS
WITH ME.

27:46.295 --> 27:47.767
ONE.

27:55.444 --> 27:57.807
YOUR BUDDY --
HE'S QUITE A JACKASS.

27:57.807 --> 27:59.178
Charlotte: JACK!

27:59.178 --> 28:01.110
I HEAR YOU GIVE HER
SO MUCH AS ASPIRIN,

28:01.110 --> 28:04.814
I'M COMING FOR YOU.

28:04.814 --> 28:10.059
NOW...LEAVE PEACEFULLY...

28:10.059 --> 28:12.191
OR I WILL ARREST YOU.

28:12.191 --> 28:13.793
BOTH OF YOU.

28:22.101 --> 28:24.073
Louise: STOP!

28:24.073 --> 28:27.136
YOU CAN'T TAKE THAT FROM ME!
THAT'S MY PRIVATE PROPERTY!

28:27.136 --> 28:28.407
SORRY, MA'AM. REGULATIONS.
 SHE WARNED YOU.

28:28.407 --> 28:29.809
HEY!
 THEY TAKE IT ALL.

28:29.809 --> 28:32.281
NO! BUT THIS ISN'T FAIR!

28:32.281 --> 28:33.382
Man: ALL RIGHT.
I'M COMING THROUGH.

28:33.382 --> 28:34.383
BACK TO YOUR ROOM.

28:34.383 --> 28:35.745
[ GRUNTS ]

29:06.115 --> 29:08.117
[ KEYPAD BEEPS ]

29:08.117 --> 29:10.319
[ ALARM BLARING ]
 HEY, WHAT'S GOING ON? HEY!

29:10.319 --> 29:13.122
HEY, WHO'S IN THERE?!

29:18.057 --> 29:19.458
OPEN THIS DOOR!

29:19.458 --> 29:23.032
FIRE! FIRE!

29:25.194 --> 29:28.197
OPEN THE DOOR!

29:28.197 --> 29:31.100
THANK YOU, OLGA.

29:31.100 --> 29:33.803
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

29:48.157 --> 29:52.091
GO, VICTORIA!
GO! GO! GO!

29:52.091 --> 29:55.024
[ KEYPAD BEEPS ]

29:55.024 --> 29:57.526
Louise: WAIT FOR ME!

30:00.269 --> 30:02.071
I'M SORRY, POPPET.

30:02.071 --> 30:04.273
NO! VICTORIA!

30:05.975 --> 30:07.877
[ DEVICE BEEPS ]

30:07.877 --> 30:09.438
[ GRUNTS ]

30:19.588 --> 30:22.091
HEY, SLOW DOWN,
PO-PO PORTER.

30:22.091 --> 30:25.154
I WANT AN INTRO
TO THAT PARTNER OF Y--

30:25.154 --> 30:27.096
HE LEFT.

30:27.096 --> 30:29.228
WHAT?
 [ PANTING ]

30:29.228 --> 30:33.132
I DON'T KNOW WHAT I WAS THINKING
BRINGING HIM HERE.

30:33.132 --> 30:36.866
THERE WAS A SITUATION
WITH CHARLOTTE.

30:36.866 --> 30:39.038
SHE CAME HERE WITH GIDEON.

30:39.038 --> 30:40.539
THEY'RE DATING?

30:40.539 --> 30:42.011
DATING, DOING BLOW --

30:42.011 --> 30:44.173
WHATEVER YOU WANT TO CALL IT,
HE'S A BAD INFLUENCE.

30:44.173 --> 30:47.016
OH, YEAH.
HE'S A REAL ENFANT HAIR-IBLE.

30:47.016 --> 30:48.918
I CONSIDERED WORKING WITH HIM
AT ONE POINT,

30:48.918 --> 30:52.281
BUT HIS BUSINESS MODEL IS TWO
PARTS MADOFF, ONE PART MANSON.

30:52.281 --> 30:53.352
[ SIGHS ]

30:53.352 --> 30:55.254
YOU KNOW,
I USED TO BE THE ONLY PERSON

30:55.254 --> 30:56.986
CHARLOTTE COULD DEPEND ON.

30:56.986 --> 30:59.558
AT THIS RATE, I'LL BE THE --
THE ONE BOOKING HER

30:59.558 --> 31:01.090
BY THE END OF THE SUMMER.

31:06.065 --> 31:08.437
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

31:12.902 --> 31:15.504
[ SIGHS ]

31:15.504 --> 31:18.047
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

31:18.047 --> 31:21.510
OH, I WAS JUST SAYING
I WANT TO POACH YOUR GUEST LIST

31:21.510 --> 31:23.152
FOR MY NEXT FUNDRAISER.

31:23.152 --> 31:24.583
[ CHUCKLES ] FUNNY.

31:24.583 --> 31:26.956
YOUR BROTHER
SAID THE SAME.

31:26.956 --> 31:28.517
DID HE?

31:28.517 --> 31:30.089
NO.

31:30.089 --> 31:32.521
ACTUALLY, I COULDN'T UNDERSTAND
A WORD HE WAS SAYING.

31:32.521 --> 31:34.163
HE WAS SO HIGH ON YAYO.

31:34.163 --> 31:36.966
DID YOU KNOW
THAT HE BROUGHT CHARLOTTE?

31:36.966 --> 31:39.428
THAT'S AN INTERESTING CHOICE,
IF YOU ASK ME --

31:39.428 --> 31:41.400
HIM GOING AFTER
DANIEL'S SISTER.

31:41.400 --> 31:42.601
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

31:42.601 --> 31:45.674
UH,
I'M NOT SURE YOU HEARD,

31:45.674 --> 31:49.378
BUT CHARLIE DID A STINT IN REHAB
AFTER AN OVERDOSE.

31:49.378 --> 31:53.442
SHE'S NOT THE MOST STABLE
LITTLE PONY.

31:53.442 --> 31:55.344
I DIDN'T REALIZE.

31:55.344 --> 31:57.916
JUST GIVEN HER HISTORY,
IT MAKES ME WONDER

31:57.916 --> 31:59.388
WHAT GIDEON WANTS WITH HER,

31:59.388 --> 32:02.451
AS IF SQUEEZING HER BROTHER
OUT OF LeMARCHAL WASN'T ENOUGH.

32:02.451 --> 32:05.454
DANIEL STEPPED DOWN
OF HIS OWN VOLITION.

32:05.454 --> 32:07.096
DID HE?

32:07.096 --> 32:08.297
MM-HMM.

32:08.297 --> 32:10.199
HMM.

32:10.199 --> 32:13.662
THEN I'M AFRAID
I'VE SUCCUMBED TO IDLE GOSSIP.

32:15.304 --> 32:19.108
ALTHOUGH, NOW I AM CURIOUS
WHAT DANIEL WOULD SAY

32:19.108 --> 32:22.571
IF YOU ASKED HIM ABOUT
HIS NIGHT WITH THE REDHEAD.

32:30.119 --> 32:32.151
Emily:
I'VE HEARD THE WHISPERS --

32:32.151 --> 32:34.553
PEOPLE WONDERING
WHY I BOUGHT THIS HOUSE,

32:34.553 --> 32:37.586
HOW COULD I LIVE HERE KNOWING
WHAT CONRAD GRAYSON DID.

32:37.586 --> 32:40.159
WELL, CALL ME AN OPTIMIST,

32:40.159 --> 32:43.962
BUT I SAW AN OPPORTUNITY
TO TAKE SOMETHING DARK

32:43.962 --> 32:46.535
AND BREATHE NEW LIFE INTO IT --
MAKE GOOD HAPPEN,

32:46.535 --> 32:48.197
WHICH ALL OF YOU
HAVE HELPED ME DO TODAY

32:48.197 --> 32:49.198
WITH YOUR GENEROUS DONATIONS.

32:49.198 --> 32:50.199
SO THANK YOU.

32:50.199 --> 32:51.600
[ APPLAUSE ]

32:51.600 --> 32:53.272
HEAR, HEAR!

32:53.272 --> 32:55.644
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

32:55.644 --> 32:57.606
IN THAT SAME SPIRIT
OF STARTING ANEW,

32:57.606 --> 32:59.648
WE INVITED
THE SOUTHAMPTON YACHT CLUB

32:59.648 --> 33:02.311
TO CHRISTEN THIS VESSEL, WHICH
LAUNCHES FROM THE GOLD COAST

33:02.311 --> 33:05.014
ON FRIDAY FOR HER MAIDEN RACE.

33:05.014 --> 33:07.486
I'LL LET HER CAPTAIN
TAKE IT FROM HERE.

33:07.486 --> 33:10.089
THANKS, EMILY.

33:10.089 --> 33:12.161
THANKS, EVERYONE,
FOR BEING HERE.

33:12.161 --> 33:13.192
HAPPY MEMORIAL DAY.

33:13.192 --> 33:15.124
WHAT A WAY TO CELEBRATE, HUH?

33:15.124 --> 33:16.595
All: YEAH!

33:16.595 --> 33:21.330
MY CREW LEFT ME WITH THE CHOICE
OF NAMING THIS LOVELY LADY.

33:21.330 --> 33:26.135
I KNEW I WANTED TO DEDICATE HER
TO THE LOVE OF MY LIFE,

33:26.135 --> 33:29.678
MY ANCHOR WHEN I'M ADRIFT.

33:29.678 --> 33:31.340
BOYS.

33:31.340 --> 33:34.043
[ APPLAUSE ]

33:35.284 --> 33:36.685
VALERIE?

33:36.685 --> 33:39.048
YOU SON OF A BITCH. YOU NAMED
THE BOAT AFTER YOUR MISTRESS?

33:39.048 --> 33:40.689
NO, THAT'S NOT --
I DIDN'T DO THAT.

33:40.689 --> 33:42.691
YOU'RE STILL SCREWING HER,
AREN'T YOU?!

33:42.691 --> 33:43.752
NO!
 [ GASPS ]

33:43.752 --> 33:45.254
AFTER EVERYTHING
YOU PUT ME THROUGH.

33:45.254 --> 33:46.525
NO, THEY PAINTED
THE WRONG NAME.

33:46.525 --> 33:48.057
NO, OR YOUR SAID THE WRONG NAME
BY ACCIDENT.

33:48.057 --> 33:49.098
WOULDN'T BE THE FIRST TIME
THAT HAPPENED.

33:49.098 --> 33:50.699
JEN, FOR GOD'S SAKE,
DON'T DO THIS.

33:50.699 --> 33:54.032
I ONLY GAVE YOU AN ALIBI
TO SAVE MYSELF THE HUMILIATION.

33:56.605 --> 33:59.208
BUT NOW YOU CAN TELL EVERYONE
FOR YOURSELF...

33:59.208 --> 34:00.609
OH, FOR GOD'S SAKE.

34:00.609 --> 34:02.471
...HOW YOU KILLED
THIS POOR GIRL'S FIANCé

34:02.471 --> 34:05.614
BECAUSE YOU WERE TOO BUSY
PILOTING YOUR WHORE

34:05.614 --> 34:07.076
INSTEAD OF YOUR BOAT.

34:08.677 --> 34:10.549
I AM SO SORRY.
[ SOBS ]

34:10.549 --> 34:12.581
JEN! JEN!

34:12.581 --> 34:15.123
You crashed into that girl's car
on purpose.

34:15.123 --> 34:17.686
I came across her story,
and I wanted to make it right.

34:17.686 --> 34:19.688
It worked.
 Whoa, wait. What worked?

34:19.688 --> 34:21.059
Manipulating retaliation
for a girl

34:21.059 --> 34:22.291
that did not even ask
for it?

34:22.291 --> 34:23.762
You wouldn't understand.
She will.

34:27.235 --> 34:29.138
NANCY.

34:29.138 --> 34:31.540
NANCY, PLEASE WAIT.

34:31.540 --> 34:32.801
LOOK, I'M SORRY.

34:32.801 --> 34:35.174
I HAD NO IDEA
THAT YOUR FIANCé --

34:35.174 --> 34:37.576
HE WAS THE ONE
WHO WAS KILLED LAST YEAR.

34:37.576 --> 34:41.250
[ Crying ] YOU KNOW
WHEN YOU HIT MY CAR?

34:41.250 --> 34:43.782
IT WAS KIND OF
THE BEST THING

34:43.782 --> 34:47.356
THAT HAD HAPPENED TO ME
IN A LONG TIME.

34:47.356 --> 34:51.860
IT FELT GOOD TO GET UPSET
ABOUT SOMETHING SO TRIVIAL.

34:51.860 --> 34:54.422
FOR SO LONG,
I COULDN'T FEEL ANYTHING

34:54.422 --> 34:56.824
BUT HATRED
FOR THAT MAN OUT THERE.

34:56.824 --> 34:59.498
I GOT SICK OF HATING.

34:59.498 --> 35:02.471
IT IS A USELESS,
CRIPPLING EMOTION.

35:02.471 --> 35:04.303
AT LEAST NOW
HE'LL BE CHARGED.

35:04.303 --> 35:05.434
THEN WHAT?

35:05.434 --> 35:08.377
HE'S GONNA HIRE FANCY LAWYERS
TO FIGHT IT.

35:08.377 --> 35:09.808
IF THERE'S A TRIAL,

35:09.808 --> 35:12.311
I-IT WOULD TAKE MONTHS
IF NOT YEARS, RIGHT?

35:12.311 --> 35:17.216
WHILE I LIVE TH-THE WORST DAY
OF MY LIFE OVER AND OVER AGAIN.

35:17.216 --> 35:20.189
EVEN IF THEY FIND HIM GUILTY,
WHAT'S IT ALL FOR?

35:20.189 --> 35:25.354
NOTHING CAN BRING BACK
THE PEOPLE WE LOVE.

35:25.354 --> 35:27.556
NOTHING.

35:35.234 --> 35:37.166
[ SIGHS ]

35:37.166 --> 35:39.238
I'M SORRY.
WHAT WERE YOU EXPECTING?

35:39.238 --> 35:40.269
A "THANK YOU"?

35:40.269 --> 35:41.370
LEAVE ME ALONE.

35:41.370 --> 35:43.342
I ALREADY MADE
THAT MISTAKE.

35:43.342 --> 35:46.215
ADDICTS CANNOT BE TRUSTED
TO BE BY THEMSELVES.

35:46.215 --> 35:49.178
I'M NOT AN ADDICT.

35:49.178 --> 35:51.180
YOU ARE
THE VERY DEFINITION!

35:51.180 --> 35:54.423
EMS, I HAVE BEEN HERE
SINCE THE BEGINNING,

35:54.423 --> 35:56.154
BUT YOU SHUT ME OUT

35:56.154 --> 35:58.887
JUST LIKE YOU'RE
SHUTTING ME OUT NOW.

35:58.887 --> 36:02.791
WHY? BECAUSE YOU'RE ASHAMED
OR -- OR IN DENIAL?

36:02.791 --> 36:04.493
EITHER WAY...

36:04.493 --> 36:05.834
[ DOORKNOB RATTLES ]
 [ GRUNTS ]

36:05.834 --> 36:08.166
...EM, YOU'RE SCARING
THE HELL OUT OF ME.

36:08.166 --> 36:11.440
MAYBE IT'S TIME
FOR AN INTERVENTION

36:11.440 --> 36:13.842
TO FORCE YOU TO BE
WHO YOU REALLY ARE.

36:13.842 --> 36:16.505
WHAT IF I WENT OUT THERE
AND TOLD EVERYBODY

36:16.505 --> 36:18.877
THAT AMANDA CLARKE
IS ALIVE AND WELL?

36:18.877 --> 36:20.949
AND EVERYONE SHE LOVED
IS DEAD.

36:20.949 --> 36:22.911
THE GRAYSONS
KILLED THEM ALL.

36:22.911 --> 36:24.953
THEY LEFT ME NOTHING
TO GO BACK TO, NOLAN.

36:24.953 --> 36:26.415
THIS IS ALL I HAVE LEFT.

36:26.415 --> 36:29.588
THAT'S WHY YOU CAN'T LET GO
OF EMILY THORNE.

36:31.890 --> 36:32.961
EMS...

36:32.961 --> 36:35.864
GET OUT.

36:44.673 --> 36:46.975
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

36:46.975 --> 36:49.978
ONE PEACE OFFERING
DESERVES ANOTHER,

36:49.978 --> 36:51.980
UNLESS YOU'RE
OFF NEGRONIS NOW.

36:51.980 --> 36:53.982
I ONLY SAID THAT
SO YOU WOULD LET ME UP.

36:53.982 --> 36:56.745
WHY DID YOU REALLY STEP DOWN
FROM LeMARCHAL?

36:56.745 --> 36:59.288
THIS AGAIN?
I ALREADY TOLD YOU.

36:59.288 --> 37:00.889
NO, YOU DIDN'T, ACTUALLY.

37:00.889 --> 37:03.392
YOU CITED
YOUR FAMILY'S TRAGEDIES,

37:03.392 --> 37:06.255
BUT FAMILY NEVER STOPPED
DANIEL GRAYSON BEFORE.

37:06.255 --> 37:08.226
AND I KNOW YOU
JUST LIKE YOU KNOW

37:08.226 --> 37:10.959
I'VE NEVER BEEN SATISFIED
WITH HALF-TRUTHS.

37:10.959 --> 37:13.862
SO TELL ME ABOUT
THE REDHEAD.

37:13.862 --> 37:15.904
[ SCOFFS ]

37:15.904 --> 37:17.966
WHAT DID GIDEON SAY?

37:17.966 --> 37:20.409
I WANT TO HEAR IT FROM YOU.

37:20.409 --> 37:23.572
[ SIGHS ] OKAY.

37:26.975 --> 37:30.549
REMEMBER THAT NIGHT I INVITED
YOU OVER TO THE SASSEN HOTEL?

37:30.549 --> 37:32.981
AND CANCELLED
TWO MINUTES LATER? YES.

37:32.981 --> 37:37.656
I'D BEEN PARTYING
WITH THIS GIRL -- THE REDHEAD --

37:37.656 --> 37:40.859
AND I MUST'VE PASSED OUT.

37:40.859 --> 37:45.764
AND WHEN I WOKE UP,
I FOUND HER O.D.'d.

37:45.764 --> 37:50.268
ALL I COULD THINK
AT THE TIME

37:50.268 --> 37:51.840
WAS WHAT THIS WOULD DO
TO ME,

37:51.840 --> 37:54.973
WHAT THIS WOULD DO TO MY NAME,
YOUR COMPANY.

37:57.546 --> 37:59.378
SO I TOOK CARE OF IT.

37:59.378 --> 38:02.010
SO YOU "TOOK CARE OF IT."

38:04.413 --> 38:07.386
AND, UH, WHAT ROLE
DID GIDEON PLAY IN THIS?

38:07.386 --> 38:08.717
NO. WHAT DID HE TELL YOU?

38:08.717 --> 38:10.058
OH, IT DOESN'T MATTER
WHAT HE TOLD ME. AND THAT --

38:10.058 --> 38:12.290
OH, SO HE DIDN'T TELL YOU
ANYTHING. UNBELIEVABLE.

38:12.290 --> 38:14.062
ANSWER THE QUESTION.

38:14.062 --> 38:15.894
WHAT I DIDN'T KNOW
AT THE TIME

38:15.894 --> 38:18.026
WAS THAT GIDEON WAS THERE
WHEN SHE DIED.

38:18.026 --> 38:21.069
HE TOOK A PHOTO OF HER
AND USED IT TO BLACKMAIL ME

38:21.069 --> 38:22.931
AND FORCE ME
OUT OF LeMARCHAL.

38:22.931 --> 38:24.403
NOW, I DIDN'T TELL YOU

38:24.403 --> 38:26.505
BECAUSE I WANTED TO PROTECT YOU
FROM MY MISTAKES.

38:26.505 --> 38:29.408
NOW, YES, WHAT I DID
WAS INDEFENSIBLE.

38:29.408 --> 38:31.009
YES,
I SHOULD'VE CALLED THE COPS.

38:31.009 --> 38:33.542
BUT I DON'T -- I DON'T KNOW.
I -- I PANICKED.

38:33.542 --> 38:36.945
IT SEEMS THAT'S WHAT HE WAS
COUNTING ON.

38:36.945 --> 38:39.418
AS IF HE HAD PLANNED IT.

38:40.919 --> 38:44.493
HE GOT THE ROOM THAT NIGHT.
HE PICKED THE GIRL.

38:44.493 --> 38:46.995
PART OF ME
HAS ALWAYS WONDERED

38:46.995 --> 38:49.998
IF HE JUST GOT LUCKY
SHE O.D.'d, OR...

38:49.998 --> 38:52.030
YOU THINK
MY BROTHER KILLED HER.

38:54.102 --> 38:55.934
THEN WE HAVE TO DO
SOMETHING.

38:55.934 --> 38:57.666
NOT ME. I'M DONE WITH HIM.

38:57.666 --> 38:59.408
WELL, ARE YOU DONE
WITH YOUR SISTER?

38:59.408 --> 39:03.912
BECAUSE CHARLOTTE IS WITH HIM
RIGHT NOW.

39:03.912 --> 39:05.414
[ MOANS ]

39:07.816 --> 39:09.948
HEY, SLOW DOWN.
LEAVE SOME FOR ME.

39:09.948 --> 39:13.582
I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE
JACK RUINED THE REST.

39:13.582 --> 39:16.084
JACK IS A GUTLESS DOUCHEBAG,
LIKE ALL COPS,

39:16.084 --> 39:18.787
WHO HIDES BEHIND HIS BADGE
AND HIS GUN.

39:18.787 --> 39:22.030
THAT'S JUST IT.
HE THINKS HE'S UNTOUCHABLE NOW.

39:22.030 --> 39:24.993
LET ME TELL YOU SOMETHING,
SWEETHEART.

39:24.993 --> 39:29.768
NO ONE IS UNTOUCHABLE.

39:32.941 --> 39:34.943
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

39:34.943 --> 39:35.974
Nolan: HELLO?

39:35.974 --> 39:37.676
EMILY: Can we talk?

39:37.676 --> 39:39.678
WELL, THAT DEPENDS.

39:39.678 --> 39:43.111
ARE WE MAKING UP OR...
BREAKING UP?

39:43.111 --> 39:45.684
STOP.

39:45.684 --> 39:48.857
LOOK, I'M SORRY THAT I WASN'T
HONEST WITH YOU TODAY.

39:48.857 --> 39:51.990
You asked me
why I did what I did.

39:51.990 --> 39:54.022
[ SIGHS ]

39:56.825 --> 40:00.068
I EMPATHIZED
WITH NANCY.

40:02.070 --> 40:05.634
I WANTED TO PROTECT HER FROM
FEELING THE PAIN THAT I FELT.

40:05.634 --> 40:08.677
From becoming like me.

40:08.677 --> 40:11.910
SHE WAS NEVER LIKE ME.

40:11.910 --> 40:13.712
NO ONE IS.

40:13.712 --> 40:16.044
YOU'RE A SNOWFLAKE --

40:16.044 --> 40:22.120
A UNIQUE,
BLOODTHIRSTY SNOWFLAKE.

40:22.120 --> 40:25.554
AND THAT'S JUST IT,
ISN'T IT?

40:25.554 --> 40:28.827
LIKE YOU SAID,
I'M AN ADDICT.

40:28.827 --> 40:34.533
That thirst
has become a part of me.

40:34.533 --> 40:38.607
I DON'T KNOW WHO I AM
WITHOUT IT.

40:40.969 --> 40:43.141
MAYBE I DON'T WANT TO.

40:43.141 --> 40:45.674
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

40:45.674 --> 40:48.076
[ SIGHS ]
LET ME CALL YOU BACK.

41:00.729 --> 41:03.892
OH, YOU DIDN'T INVITE ME
TO YOUR PARTY.

41:03.892 --> 41:06.665
HOW DID YOU GET OUT,
VICTORIA?

41:06.665 --> 41:08.897
WITH A LITTLE HELP
FROM MY FRIENDS.

41:08.897 --> 41:12.040
NOTHING BONDS PEOPLE LIKE
BEING IMPRISONED TOGETHER --

41:12.040 --> 41:14.943
SOMETHING I KNOW YOU'RE FAMILIAR
WITH, GIVEN YOUR TIME IN JUVIE.

41:16.044 --> 41:17.806
AM I RIGHT, AMANDA?

41:17.806 --> 41:19.778
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

41:19.778 --> 41:22.010
ARRIVING HERE TONIGHT,

41:22.010 --> 41:24.012
I THINK I KNOW
HOW YOU MUST'VE FELT

41:24.012 --> 41:26.254
WHEN YOU FIRST RETURNED
TO THE HAMPTONS.

41:26.254 --> 41:28.957
SO MUCH HATRED IN YOUR HEART
FOR ME

41:28.957 --> 41:30.018
AND WHAT YOU THOUGHT
I'D DONE.

41:30.018 --> 41:31.059
WHAT YOU DID.

41:31.059 --> 41:33.662
IF YOU'D ONLY
COME CLEAN THEN,

41:33.662 --> 41:35.794
YOU COULD'VE KNOWN
THE TRUTH.

41:35.794 --> 41:38.196
YOU COULD'VE REUNITED
WITH YOUR SISTER

41:38.196 --> 41:40.599
AND PREVENTED HER
SO MUCH PAIN,

41:40.599 --> 41:44.202
BUT INSTEAD,
YOU CHOSE REVENGE.

41:46.104 --> 41:48.677
NOW IT'S MY TURN.

41:48.677 --> 41:51.940
THEN WELCOME BACK.

42:03.692 --> 42:05.754
[ MUFFLED SCREAMING ]

42:08.126 --> 42:10.799
[ PANTING ]

42:10.799 --> 42:14.032
[ MUFFLED SPEAKING ]
